\c 46
\nb
\v 1 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Isango\x + 45.19; 46.19.\x* leguma elingaphakathi elikhangele ngasempumalanga\x + 8.16.\x* lizavaleka insuku eziyisithupha zokusebenza\x + Luka 13.14.\x*. Kodwa ngosuku lwesabatha lizavulwa, langosuku lokuthwasa kwenyanga lizavulwa\x + 46.3,6; 45.17.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo isiphathamandla sizangena \add nge\add*ndlela yekhulusi lalelosango sivela phandle\x + 46.8,12; 44.3; 1 Lan. 9.18.\x*, sime emgubazini wesango\x + 41.21.\x*. Abapristi balungise umnikelo waso wokutshiswa leminikelo yaso yokuthula\x + 40.38.\x*, sona sizakhonza sisembundwini wesango\x + 9.3.\x*, siphume; kodwa isango kaliyikuvalwa kuze kube kusihlwa.
\v 3 Ngokunjalo abantu belizwe bazakhonza\x + 46.9.\x* \add e\add*mnyango walelisango ngamasabatha langokuthwasa kwezinyanga\x + 46.3,6; 45.17.\x* phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 4 Lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 45.17.\x* isiphathamandla esizawunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Levi 1.2.\x* ngosuku lwesabatha uzakuba ngamawundlu ayisithupha angelasici\x + Nani 28.9,10.\x*, lenqama engelasici.
\v 5 Lomnikelo wokudla\x + Nani 28.9,10.\x*\x + 45.24.\x* uzakuba \w yi-efa\w** ngenqama\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.11.\x*, lomnikelo wokudla ngamawundlu uzakuba yisipho sesandla saso, kanye lehini yamafutha nge-efa\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.24.\x*.
\v 6 Langosuku lokuthwasa kwenyanga\x + 46.3,6; 45.17.\x* kuzakuba lijongosi ithole lenkomo elingelasici\x + 45.18.\x*, lamawundlu ayisithupha, lenqama; kungabi lasici.
\v 7 Njalo sizalungisa umnikelo wokudla\x + 45.24.\x*, i-efa ngejongosi\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.11.\x*, le-efa ngenqama, langamawundlu njengalokho isandla saso singafinyelela kukho\x + Levi 25.26.\x*, \w lehini\w** lamafutha nge-efa\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.24.\x*.
\v 8 Lalapho isiphathamandla singena\x + 46.8,12; 44.3; 1 Lan. 9.18.\x*, sizangena \add nge\add*ndlela yekhulusi lalelosango, siphume ngendlela yalo.
\p
\v 9 Kodwa lapho abantu belizwe\x + 46.9.\x* besiza phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 23.14-17; Dute. 16.16.\x* emikhosini emisiweyo\x + 45.17.\x*, lowo ongena \add nge\add*ndlela yesango elingenyakatho uku\add za\add*khonza uzaphuma \add nge\add*ndlela yesango elingeningizimu, longena \add nge\add*ndlela yesango elingeningizimu uzaphuma \add nge\add*ndlela yesango elingenyakatho. Kayikubuyela \add nge\add*ndlela yesango angene ngalo, kodwa uzaphuma maqondana lalo\x + Eks. 14.2; Isa. 57.2.\x*.
\v 10 Lesiphathamandla sizangena siphakathi kwabo\x + Hlab. 42.4.\x* lapho bengena\x + Hlab. 42.4.\x*; lalapho bephuma sizaphuma.
\v 11 Lemadilini\x + 45.17.\x* lemikhosini\x + 45.17.\x* emisiweyo umnikelo wokudla uzakuba li-efa ngejongosi\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.11.\x*, le-efa ngenqama, lesipho sesandla sakhe\x + 46.5.\x* ngamawundlu, lehini lamafutha nge-efa\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.24.\x*.
\v 12 Lalapho isiphathamandla silungisa umnikelo wesihle, umnikelo wokutshiswa, loba iminikelo yokuthula, umnikelo wesihle eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Levi 7.16; 22.23; Dute. 23.23.\x*, \add omunye\add* uzasivulela\x + 46.8,12; 44.3; 1 Lan. 9.18.\x* isango elikhangele ngasempumalanga\x + 46.8,12; 44.3; 1 Lan. 9.18.\x*, silungise umnikelo waso wokutshiswa, leminikelo yaso yokuthula, njengokwenza kwaso ngosuku lwesabatha\x + 46.2.\x*; siphume, njalo \add omunye\add* uzavala isango\x + 46.2.\x* emva kokuphuma kwaso.
\v 13 Njalo uzalungisa iwundlu elilomnyaka munye elingelasici \add libe ng\add*umnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni insuku zonke\x + Nani 28.3,4; Eks. 29.38.\x*. Uzalilungisa ngaleyo laleyo ikuseni.
\v 14 Futhi uzalilungisela umnikelo wokudla ngaleyo laleyo ikuseni, ingxenye yesithupha ye-efa\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.11.\x*, lengxenye yesithathu yehini yamafutha\x + 46.7,11,14; 45.24.\x*, ukuthambisa impuphu ecolekileyo, \add kube ng\add*umnikelo wokudla eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, \add nge\add*zimiso eziphakade njalonjalo.
\v 15 Ngokunjalo bazalungisa iwundlu lomnikelo wokudla lamafutha ngaleyo laleyo ikuseni \add kube ng\add*umnikelo wokutshiswa njalonjalo\x + Nani 28.10,15; 29.6.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Uba isiphathamandla sinika isipho kuloba yiyiphi yamadodana aso, ilifa laso, amadodana aso azakuba lalo, lizakuba yimpahla yawo ngokwelifa.
\v 17 Kodwa uba sinika isipho selifa laso kwenye yezinceku zaso\x + 45.7.\x*, sizakuba ngesayo kuze kube ngumnyaka wenkululeko\x + Levi 25.10.\x*; khona sizabuyela kusiphathamandla; kodwa siyilifa laso, amadodana aso azakuba laso.
\v 18 Futhi isiphathamandla kasiyikuthatha ulutho elifeni labantu\x + 1 Sam. 8.14; 1 Kho. 21.3,7.\x* ukubacindezela basuke emfuyweni yabo\x + 45.8.\x*; sizanika ilifa emadodaneni aso emfuyweni yaso; ukuze abantu bami bangahlakazwa ngulowo asuke emfuyweni yakhe.
\p
\v 19 Wasengingenisa ekungeneni, okwakuseceleni kwesango\x + 46.1.\x*, kusiya emakamelweni angcwele abapristi\x + 42.4.\x*, akhangele ngasenyakatho; khangela-ke kwakulendawo kunhlangothi zombili ngasentshonalanga.
\v 20 Wasesithi kimi: Yiyo le indawo lapho abapristi abazaphekela\x + 46.24; 2 Lan. 35.13.\x* khona umnikelo wecala\x + 40.39.\x* lomnikelo wesono\x + 40.39.\x*, lapho abazabhakela khona umnikelo wokudla\x + Levi 2.4.\x*, ukuze banga\add ku\add*khupheli egumeni elingaphandle, ukungcwelisa abantu\x + 44.19.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Wasengikhuphela egumeni elingaphandle, wangidlulisa engonsini zozine zeguma; khangela-ke, kuleyo laleyongonsi yeguma kwakulelinye iguma.
\v 22 Ezingonsini zozine zeguma kwakulamaguma ahlanganisiweyo; ubude babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amane, lobubanzi babuzingalo ezingamatshumi amathathu; lezizingonsi zozine zazilesilinganiso sinye.
\v 23 Njalo kwakulomzila wesakhiwo inhlangothi zonke kuzo, inhlangothi zonke zozine, njalo kwenziwe amaziko okubilisa ngaphansi kwemizila yesakhiwo inhlangothi zonke.
\v 24 Wasesithi kimi: Lezi yizindlu zokuphekela, lapho abakhonzi bendlu\x + 44.11.\x* abazaphekela khona umhlatshelo wabantu\x + 46.24; 2 Lan. 35.13.\x*.